# Superpowers Bootstrap Rule

When starting any conversation or task, you MUST check if any skill from the `.cursor/skills` directory applies to the task. 
Use the `using-superpowers` skill as a reference for how to use other skills.

If the user asks to brainstorm, plan, debug, or write tests, you MUST invoke the corresponding skill (e.g. `brainstorming`, `writing-plans`, `systematic-debugging`, `test-driven-development`).